reviews.review_text: my first I love it! That fact that I can relive or at least rehear my first Dead show from when I was 16 years old. I smuggled paper under a bandaid acsross the border. I recall my bro and I were stopped and asked if we had anything to declare and as the columbian roach smoldered in our ashtray of our 66 Plymouth Valiant, I declared I was Canadian man. Time were easier then pre 9 11 but the war on drugs was risng its evil head (thanks Nancy). We got a pass into the States and it was a pleasant surprise.
